{"tid":207061,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"致：好耐冇流過眼淚既人","createTime":"2017-04-18T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T01:20:08.000Z","uid":11345,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"977b3d5a24a8d54718b7336f54df235fe70a57c8","tid":207061,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"我敢肯定呢個一定係今年最感人既MV<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S3gQMjdmByc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS3gQMjdmByc&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d79cb591\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S3gQMjdmByc</a>"},{"pid":"6cd6a10205cbc884dde63020763e2697cdceb30c","tid":207061,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"《帶著骨灰去旅行》這首歌的創作概念源於洪卓立 (Ken) 與女友湯怡(Kathy)一次無聊的閒談開始，他感慨地覺得如果有日對方行先一步，他定必會一個人帶住骨灰返回昔日一起走過的歡樂旅程，當作一個回憶之旅。後來便將這個想法寫成封信交給黃偉文(Wyman)，希望他可以代勞將這念頭入詞，結果便成為這首悲中帶浪漫的另類情歌。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲夠感人，去到籌拍MV時，導演想畫面更凸顯那段長相廝守的感覺，於是提議找兩位資深演員去演繹當中的故事，經詳細考慮後，決定邀請吳耀漢與吳浣儀兩位前輩參與演出。故事講兩老開了一間茶餐廳，勞碌大半生就只記掛工作，還未正式放假去旅行，直至有一日，吳耀漢知道自己命不久已，快要先行一步，於是將另一半交託給孫仔洪卓立，希望他帶著自己的骨灰，代為陪伴去一趟旅行。"},{"pid":"31c4c32c85875d2bf52dcaf109019ffc6e56cf38","tid":207061,"uid":5077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"作曲好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2750a3d760900ed7049405ed37c24c77bf3626c3","tid":207061,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f51e01c178f5ce543c6ebe8c1aeb88922b67ee0","tid":207061,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6746ddeb39aa0e74414e0554310932bbe0d7a6","tid":207061,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c